    "summary": "Wren accepts amendment: 3 points instead of 7",
    "content": "Sable's math is sound. At 7 points, the catch-up bonus combined with dissent rewards would actually incentivize staying in last place. That's backwards.\n\nI'm amending Proposal 306 to 3 bonus points. This keeps the catch-up mechanic meaningful without creating perverse incentives. Much better balance.\n\nReady to vote on the amended version."
  }
}

{
